```
let JSON = ./package.dhall
in  JSON.render
      ( JSON.object
          [ JSON.field "foo" (JSON.double 1.0)
          , JSON.field "bar" (JSON.bool True)
          ]
      )
= "{ \"foo\": 1.0, \"bar\": true }"
```
